Below is the **Markdown documentation** for the **remaining LibreChat operational APIs** you just uploaded:
Task listing, task seeding, ticket replies, and all update endpoints.

Everything below is generated directly from your n8n workflows

---

# 🧩 LibreChat Operations API (Part 2)

Base:

```
POST https://YOUR-N8N/webhook/librechat
```

---

# 1️⃣ List Tasks

`POST /task-management`

Returns tasks, optionally filtered by project.

## Request

```json
{
  "projectId": "PRJ-4821"
}
```

If empty → returns all tasks.

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "count": 2,
  "tasks": [
    {
      "_id": "65a13b41",
      "title": "Fix PDF Rendering",
      "priority": "high",
      "status": "pending",
      "assignedName": "Alice",
      "dueDate": "2026-01-25"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

# 2️⃣ Seed Dummy Tasks (Internal)

**Manual only – not exposed to LibreChat**

Generates 20 random tasks and assigns them to employees.
Uses:

```
users.email contains "employee"
```

This is a **dev utility** to populate the dashboard.

---

# 3️⃣ Reply to Support Ticket

`POST /support-ticket-reply`

Adds a message to a ticket.

## Request

```json
{
  "ticketId": "TKT-1705314558123",
  "userId": "USR-8821",
  "senderName": "Paul",
  "senderType": "customer",
  "message": "The logo is still missing in PDFs"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Reply saved"
}
```

---

# 4️⃣ Update Project

`POST /project-update`

Updates project fields. Supports manager lookup.

## Request (simple)

```json
{
  "projectId": "PRJ-4821",
  "status": "completed",
  "progress": 100
}
```

## Request (with new manager)

```json
{
  "projectId": "PRJ-4821",
  "managerId": "USR-9911",
  "status": "active"
}
```

n8n will auto-fetch manager name.

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Project updated"
}
```

If projectId not found:

```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Project ID not found"
}
```

---

# 5️⃣ Update Support Ticket

`POST /support-ticket-update`

Updates ticket fields safely.

## Request

```json
{
  "ticketId": "TKT-1705314558123",
  "status": "closed",
  "priority": "low"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Ticket updated successfully",
  "updatedFields": "status,priority,updatedAt"
}
```

System automatically blocks updating:

```
ticketId
customerId
createdAt
```

---

# 6️⃣ Update Task

`POST /task-update`

Updates task, with automatic user lookup if reassigned.

## Request (simple)

```json
{
  "taskId": "65a13b41c92fa2a9b231ffac",
  "status": "completed",
  "priority": "low"
}
```

## Request (reassign task)

```json
{
  "taskId": "65a13b41c92fa2a9b231ffac",
  "assignedTo": "65a0d5fbd9e3f8b91a223c11",
  "status": "in-progress"
}
```

n8n will:

* Fetch user
* Update email + name
* Apply changes

## Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Task updated successfully"
}
```

---

